Package ru.postgrespro.perf.pgmicrobench.statanalyzer.distributions.recognition

Class CramerVonMises

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.postgrespro.perf.pgmicrobench.statanalyzer.distributions.recognition.CramerVonMises
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDistributionTest, IParameterEstimator
    public class CramerVonMises
extends Object
implements IDistributionTest, IParameterEstimator
    This class provides methods to perform the Cramer–Von Mises test for goodness of fit and to fit a distribution to a given dataset using the Cramer–Von Mises statistic.
